{"tid":654951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解用Mac唔用Window","createTime":"2018-05-06T05:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T06:07:09.000Z","uid":167013,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0703d4c0f44e3300f41d59880fc8daa5be6e0b8e","tid":654951,"uid":167013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:58:04.000Z","msg":"其實唔係做開production嘅人用Mac，淨係用MS Word, Excel, Powerpoint, 頂盡加埋個Google Chrome嘅人點解唔用window呢, 比成倍價錢買部window都有一樣功能嘅機會否太on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTrackpad gesture同keyboard shortcut都未識根本就係浪費左部mac, 就算係用iphone或者ipad, 都唔係好覺啲人識用airdrop或者handoff過野去Mac, 好心就用翻window啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不能同意更多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢買Mac你吹呀"},{"pid":"48b8c133df2d13f21da9dd34ae74ccc36e13e03f","tid":654951,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"mr.a : 汪"},{"pid":"7365514d13117a8566112e2504568f940c489d69","tid":654951,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:02:57.000Z","msg":"如果你真係乜柒都唔做 淨係用office 當然windows 夠<br />\n你都知windows 幾撚柒 用一年就算部機幾勁都好都會慢 mac 就冇呢個問題"},{"pid":"4884eb0ecc3905635b02d24c4fc4e2d5774e45d9","tid":654951,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"睇你第一句已經知你傻閪<br />\n你估十年前咩"}]}